latestPosts.caption:
Hyaluronic Acid & ceramides to moisturise your skin? Nope. 👎🏻

With Spark Change, we’ve gone a step ahead & added ingredients that help your skin produce Hyaluronic acid & ceramides naturally, as opposed to giving you a topical ingredient to apply. 🤍

Which is why when you use Spark Change, you notice your skin feeling a LOT more hydrated and bouncy than usual. Because we’re all about letting your skin do the work for you. ✨
